+# Phase 5: Worktree Exemplar — Tasks & Context Brief
+
+**Plan**: [global-state-system-plan.md](../../global-state-system-plan.md)
+**Phase**: Phase 5: Worktree Exemplar
+**Generated**: 2026-02-27
+**Status**: Pending
